bilingual.target: 我看到一个巨大的飞机模型。
亨利和西蒙做了一个模型。
那架白色模型飞机是她的。
我刚刚做了一个模型飞船。
这个模型飞机是用什么做的？

bilingual.source: Oh, it's under the model plane in the bookcase.
bilingual.target: 哦，它在书架上的飞机模型下面。

bilingual.source: I've just made a model spaceship for our school project.
bilingual.target: 我刚刚为我们的学校项目做了一个模型飞船。

bilingual.source: Then the guide taught us how to make a model robot.
bilingual.target: 然后导游教我们如何制作机器人模型。

bilingual.source: The best thing was visiting a model of Amelia Earhart's plane!
bilingual.target: 最棒的是参观了阿梅莉亚·埃尔哈特飞机的模型！

list.abstract: MODEL（英[ˈmɒdl]，美[ˈmɑːdl]），英文单词，作名词为模型；模式；样式，作动词为制作…的模型；塑造；当模特儿展示。短语搭配有business model（商业模式），例句有“I think everyone should try to be a good role model, even if you are not a celebrity!（我认为每个人都应该努力成为一个好的榜样，即使你不是一个名人！）”

yingyinNormal.en: It was the model for the calamity depicted in Interstellar.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这是《星际穿越》中描述的灾难模型。

yingyinNormal.en: I had three model rockets as a kid, and that was the largest space program in India.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我小时候有过三个火箭模型，那是印度最大的三个太空计划了。

yingyinNormal.en: Hobby I used to have. The Battle of the Wilderness. I spent months building a model of it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我以前的爱好，莽原之役，我花了几个月，造了一个模型。

yingyinNormal.en: He and his research partner, Dr. Kim park, have come up with a model that predicts earthquakes.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他和他的研究伙伴基姆帕克博士设计出了一个可以预测地震的理论模型。

yingyinNormal.en: This is for a full scale rocket, not a model. Well, I've adjusted the formula. Not correctly.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那是给全尺寸火箭用的，而不是给模型用的。我已经调整过配方了。没调整对。

yingyinNormal.en: Is it a house for elves and fairies? Oh, no. This is a model. The real house will be much bigger.
yingyinNormal.zh: 是给精灵和小仙子住的吗？噢，不。这是模型。真的房子可要比这个大多了。

yingyinNormal.en: And instead of standing around watching, you can help us build your smaller guidance system. And with all these new skills, you'd be able to fix any model train. You'd be the king of the train store!
yingyinNormal.zh: 与其站着傻看，你不如帮我们创建更小的导向系统。有了新的技能，你可以修好任何火车模型你将成为火车模型店之王！

yingyinNormal.en: And so for the movie, I built a mathematical model Wormhole based on Einstein's relativity equations.
yingyinNormal.zh: 因此对于这部电影，基于爱因斯坦的相对论方程式，我构建了一个数学模型虫洞。

yingyinNormal.en: These things don't make any sense! We can't even model them. These are 100 times bigger than the MBS.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这些数据根本说不通，我们甚至无法建立模型它的数量，比房贷证券要大100倍。

yingyinNormal.en: Grampy Rabbit, how did you go to the moon? I flew in the rocket. It's a bit small. This is just a model.
yingyinNormal.zh: 兔爷爷，你是怎么到月球上的？我是坐在火箭上飞过去的。这个有点小。这个只是一个模型。

yingyinNormal.en: But my model is so much cleaner, I have formulas and algorithms and χ-square and standard deviation. What do you have?
yingyinNormal.zh: 但我的模型更为清晰，我推导出了公式，算法，还有卡方检验和标准差，你有什么?

yingyinNormal.en: It's very small. Is it a house for elves and fairies? Oh, no. This is a model. The real house will be much bigger.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这个房子可真小呀。是给精灵和小仙子住的吗？噢，不。这是模型。真的房子可要比这个大多了。

yingyinNormal.en: So, I think if we want to predict the height of the wave, we need to use elasticity theory and model the lattice as one continuous flexible piece.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我觉得如果想预测起伏的高度，我们需要用到弹性理论还要将格架作为一个连续柔性块的模型。

yingyinNormal.en: You don't know the half of it. It was billed as a lively give and take on the merits of model train sizes. But it was actually a setup to intimidate weak minded spineless rubes into buying H O starter sets.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你是不知道呀，本来宣传的是说今晚将会是个针对模型火车体积的优劣而进行的现场讨论会，可实际上只是为了唬那些没定力的乡巴佬去买HO轨距的入门级火车。

yingyinNormal.en: With the theme? With the model.
yingyinNormal.zh: 拍摄主题要调整？是模特。

yingyinNormal.en: It escaped capture aboard a stolen Corellian YT model freighter.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他乘坐一艘被盗的科瑞利安YT型号运输舰逃脱了追捕。

yingyinNormal.en: What's the second model? What are you talking about? All-in-one.
yingyinNormal.zh: 第二款产品是什么？你在说什么呢？一体机

yingyinNormal.en: I don't understand. Why is he in this? He's a model, mom. Oh, wait, wait. Your boyfriend's a model?
yingyinNormal.zh: 我不明白，他怎么在这里头？他是模特，老妈。等等，你男友是模特？

yingyinNormal.en: I'm going to model u.n., but we're dining tonight, right? Butter, 7:00.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我要去模特班了，但我们一起吃晚饭是吗？在吧特，7点。

yingyinNormal.en: All right, so, shh! Tyra Banks is about to kick someone off America's Next Top Model.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好吧，大家安静！泰拉·班克斯(超模之母)马上要从全美超模大赛里踢人了。

examination_example.sentence: Denmark's fashion industry agreed last month on rules and sanctions regarding the age, health, and other characteristics of <highlight>models</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 丹麦时装业上个月就有关模特年龄、健康和其他特征的规则和制裁达成一致。

examination_example.sentence: Its lawmakers gave preliminary approval last week to a law that would make it a crime to employ ultra-thin <highlight>models</highlight> on runways.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 上周，法国的立法者初步通过了一项法律，规定雇佣过于瘦弱的模特走T台会触犯法律。

examination_example.sentence: It is trying to set voluntary standards for <highlight>models</highlight> and fashion images that rely more on peer pressure for enforcement.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 它正试图为模特和时装形象设定自愿标准，这些标准更多地依赖同行的压力来执行。

examination_example.sentence: Insurance companies, meanwhile, can base their premiums on AI <highlight>models</highlight> that more accurately access risk.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 与此同时，保险公司可以将保费建立在更准确评估风险的人工智能模型上。

examination_example.sentence: In some ways the scientific publishing <highlight>model</highlight> resembles the economy of the social internet.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 在某些方面，科学出版模式类似于社会互联网的经济。

examination_example.sentence: This impact will be hopefully through a larger group of publishing places that may want to <highlight>model</highlight> their approach after Science.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这将有望影响更大范围内的出版机构，它们可能会想要效仿《科学》杂志的方式。

sense_info_list.en: a person or thing regarded as an excellent example of a specified quality

examination_example.sentence: California's plan, which is expected to be finalized by the governor next year, should serve as a <highlight>model</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 加利福尼亚州的计划有望在明年由州长最终确定下来，该计划应该成为一个范例。

examination_example.sentence: There is nothing but some old <highlight>model</highlight> planes.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 除了一些旧模型飞机，什么都没有。

examination_example.sentence: Later, we found a similar <highlight>model</highlight> plane in a store.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 后来，我们在一家商店里发现了一架类似的模型飞机。

examination_example.sentence: When can we finish making the <highlight>model</highlight> car?
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我们什么时候能完成模型汽车的制作？

sense_info_list.en: a person or thing regarded as an excellent example of a specified quality

examination_example.sentence: Whether a celebrity is a role <highlight>model</highlight> or not, he should care about his behavior.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 无论一个名人是否是一个榜样，他都应该注意他的行为。

examination_example.sentence: Everyone should try to be a good role <highlight>model</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 每个人都应该努力成为一个好的榜样。

examination_example.sentence: Since then, Xue has been a <highlight>model</highlight> for the people around her.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 从那以后，薛一直是她身边人的榜样。

examination_example.sentence: Of course, it's difficult to give someone the job of a film star or a <highlight>model</highlight>!
examination_example.sentence_trans: 当然，给某人一个电影明星或模特的工作是很难的！

examination_example.sentence: The average <highlight>model</highlight> is 180 cm tall and weighs 53 kilos.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 模特的平均身高是180厘米，体重是53公斤。

examination_example.sentence: Tom on the TV and you'll probably see beautiful <highlight>models</highlight>, handsome actors and fit sports stars.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 汤姆在电视上，你可能会看到漂亮的模特、英俊的演员和健康的体育明星。

sense_info_list.en: a particular design or version of a product

examination_example.sentence_trans: 美国拥有的无人机中，超过一半是中国型号。
